{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_10_01",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月二日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おっと、正月早々仕事のメールか。先方も大変だなぁ\nえーっと、ⅢX宛のMV撮影日変更のお願い、か",
      "startTime": 8.4666666429,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.000182600001,
          "startTime": 7.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すぐにfranさん達に連絡しないとな\n確か、年末聞いた時は――",
      "startTime": 18.9666666429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。ⅢXはお正月、三人ともオフを\n取るんですよね？　ゆっくり休んで下さいね",
      "startTime": 27.4666666429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、厳密には決めてないけど家でゆっくり過ごします\n漫画を読んだり……いや、まだ仕事があるわね",
      "startTime": 36.3302980585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "来年の『ERFOLG』の方針を決めないと。トレンド\n予測から需要のリサーチ……まだまだやること一杯だわ",
      "startTime": 45.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お正月も大変ですね。franさん、華やかな\nイメージですし、芸能人らしく海外旅行とか行くのかと",
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ行けるならハワイでもどこでも行きたいですけど\nブランドが波に乗っている今、そんな余裕ないですよ",
      "startTime": 62.6333333095,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-dialtone-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5601.408690499994,
          "startTime": 68.234742
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、franさんだけ出ない。ああ言っていたし\n忙しいのかもな。メッセージだけでも送っておこう",
      "startTime": 73.8666666429,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7998.590747300014,
          "startTime": 77.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月三日",
      "startTime": 79.1155813616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4855799437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あれから連絡がつかない……まさか何かあったのか！？\n仕方ない、franさんのマンションに行ってみよう",
      "startTime": 86.8999999762,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7131.087493899997,
          "startTime": 88.4999999762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2297515314
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2297515314
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chime-06.m4a",
      "startTime": 91.4797515314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "franさーん！　……って、鍵が開いてる……？\nおかしい……franさん、すみません！　入ります！",
      "startTime": 97.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8420.248444800009,
          "startTime": 100.6999999762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6822912933
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6822912933
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9322912933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "う、うーん……ぐぅ……ううう……\nぐぐ、ぐぅう……",
      "startTime": 111.8999999762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ、franさんが家具の下敷きに！？\nそれにこの部屋の荒れ様……！　もしかして強盗！？",
      "startTime": 118.1999999762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.0037199101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼、ですね……\n部屋は、元々こうなんです……がくり……",
      "startTime": 126.9666666429,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6829.613425000005,
          "startTime": 129.8333333351
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8351.723142899986,
          "startTime": 131.355443053
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.355443053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今の、お腹の音……か？　まさか、空腹なだけ？\nええと、これ、昼飯用に買ったおにぎりなんですが……",
      "startTime": 139.2666564703,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7147.926417900009,
          "startTime": 139.4333231608
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.3028258722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "もぐっ、何これ、めちゃくちゃ美味しいんですけど\n{user}さん、意外とセンスありますね",
      "startTime": 151.833323137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.5428259612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした。でもなんで急に家に来たんです？\nしかも勝手に上がり込んで。連絡くらいして下さいよ",
      "startTime": 159.3666564703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すみません。連絡したんですが反応が……franさん\nいつも早めに返していただけるので不安に思いまして",
      "startTime": 168.0666585048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.0677032551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "しまった、すぐ見ます……MVの撮影予定日の変更……\nなるほど、それで安否の確認に来てくれたんですね",
      "startTime": 180.4666585048,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2465.6219401999806,
          "startTime": 174.5333251953
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、助かりました\nというか、鍵まで掛け忘れていたのね……",
      "startTime": 188.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.7295081854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、三日ぶりのご飯は五臓六腑にしみますね\nライブから数日、水だけで過ごしてたので……",
      "startTime": 199.5333383958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "み、水だけで！？　というか三日振り！？\nどうしてそんなことに……すぐ隣、コンビニですけど",
      "startTime": 207.2000050624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.1455395143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……その…………\n……これが、今の私の現状だからです",
      "startTime": 217.7000050624,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coin-03.m4a",
          "delay": 433.33233989997666,
          "startTime": 218.1333374023
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coin-03.m4a",
          "delay": 866.6656732000035,
          "startTime": 218.5666707356
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "お財布から小銭が一枚、二枚……え……？\nまさか、手持ちがこれだけしかないんですか？",
      "startTime": 227.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.6286006372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ここ最近忙し過ぎて失念していたんですよ\n銀行が年末年始、休みなのを……",
      "startTime": 234.9666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それこそコンビニがあるじゃないですか\nコンビニのATMなら年末年始でも二十四時間……",
      "startTime": 241.0666717291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_korroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "korroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.7430673044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_10_01-kor013.m4a",
